title: Photography monthly - Capture Britain (photography).pdf
description:
Photography Monthly Magazine Special Edition - Capture Britain
English | 284 Pages | True PDF | 227MB

Capture Britain is a celebration of two things, the British landscape and photographing it. We have collated a selection of 250 images, separated into 20 regions, with some amazing landscape images from readers and working professional landscape photographers. Included with each image is a brief description of the scene and an OS grid reference so you can have a go at capturing the scene in your own way. So, enjoy our guide and take a little time out to explore and plan your next landscape shooting adventure. Photography Monthly is the UK's leading magazine for digital and film photographers of all levels. Each issue is packed with inspirational images, essential technique guides and reviews of the newest photo gear.
